The tables are reproduced below (but again, the diagrams were too fragile to copy). Note that
the entire spread extends from numbered page 179 through numbered page 198. Also note that
there is no Diagram or Table &quot;I,&quot; and that although Diagram G/Table H was withdrawn, it was
printed in the Report anyway.</em></p>

